LastPass command-line client (lpass) in a small (~17 MB) multi-arch Alpine image.
lpass is the entrypoint, so `docker run ghcr.io/jasonkoopmans/lastpass-cli show <site>`
works directly. Mount a volume at /root/.lpass to persist your login across runs,
and set LPASS_DISABLE_PINENTRY=1 to feed the master password on stdin for scripts.
See the linked Documentation for login and usage examples.
